i saw her face reflected in the water below me. smiling. the water turned red as she turned away. all i could feel was the tip of the knife puncturing my flesh. there i was bled dry like worms in daylight, then kicked into the river. as i wake i see her face above me... i am lying on the ground covered in blood behind the wreckage of a car.. all i can hear is her voice telling me to come home. then she puts a gun to my head and shoots.
